<section xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>47-212</num>
  <heading>Items included in annual estimates — Expenses of Water Department.</heading>
  <text>It shall be the duty of the Mayor to include in the annual estimates of the District of Columbia estimates of the expenses of the Water Department.</text>
  <annotations>
    <annotation type="History">Mar. 3, 1881, 21 Stat. 466, ch. 134, § 1</annotation>
    <annotation doc="D.C. Law 11-254" type="History">enacted, Apr. 9, 1997, D.C. Law 11-254, § 2, 44 DCR 1575</annotation>
    <annotation type="Cross References">Tax on residents and nonresidents, credits, property taxes, see § <cite path="§47-1806.06">47-1806.06</cite>.</annotation>
    <annotation type="Cross References">Water supply, see § <cite path="§34-2401.04">34-2401.04</cite> et seq.</annotation>
    <annotation type="Prior Codifications">1981 Ed., § 47-212.</annotation>
    <annotation type="Prior Codifications">1973 Ed., § 47-210.</annotation>
  </annotations>
</section>
